-- SPEC: L18579-L18596
-- | # Runtime Semantics: CatchClauseEvaluation ( \_thrownValue\_: an ECMAScript language value, ): either a normal completion containing either an ECMAScript language value or \~empty\~, or an abrupt completion
-- |
