-- | HostPromiseRejectionTracker(\_promise\_, \*\"handle\"\*). 1. Set
-- | \_promise\_.\[\[PromiseIsHandled\]\] to \*true\*. 1. Return
-- | ThrowCompletion(\_promise\_.\[\[PromiseResult\]\]). 1. Return
