-- | MatchState. 1. Assert: \_c\_ is a MatcherContinuation. 1. Let \_Input\_
-- | be \_x\_.\[\[Input\]\]. 1. Let \_e\_ be \_x\_.\[\[EndIndex\]\]. 1. Let
